description: Wedges of sweet and juicy nectarines and peaches on a bed of crispy baby cos lettuce make this summery chicken salad sing.
keywords: Nectarine, Peach, Chicken & Baby Cos Salad
name: Nectarine, Peach, Chicken & Baby Cos Salad Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Place chicken, nectarine, peach, hazelnuts, rocket and lettuce in a large bowl and toss to combine. Divide among plates, drizzle with dressing and serve with wholegrain sourdough.
